                <div id="Challenges" class="timeline-content-section" data-year="1983">
                    <h2>Industry Challenges</h2>
                    <p>Call centres in the US face unique pressures that impact performance and profitability:</p>
                    <ul style="padding-left: 5%;padding-top: 2%;font-size: 21px;line-height: 2;list-style-type: disc;color:white;">
                        <li>
                            <b style="color:#9f5ad0">High Turnover:</b> The industry sees turnover rates as high as 30-45% annually, disrupting
                            operations and increasing costs.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <b style="color:#9f5ad0">Training Costs:</b> Onboarding new agents is time-intensive and expensive, especially
                            during peak seasons like holidays.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <b style="color:#9f5ad0">Demand Volatility:</b> Seasonal spikes (e.g., Black Friday) require rapid scaling, straining
                            resources.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <b style="color:#9f5ad0">Customer Expectations:</b>  I: Rising demand for personalized, 24/7 support challenges
                            operational efficiency.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <b style="color:#9f5ad0">Technology Integration:</b> : Adopting AI and automation to enhance service without
                            sacrificing human touch.
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>
                        At Infinite Outsourcing Solutions, we understand these challenges. Our solutions are designed
                        to streamline your operations, reduce costs, and deliver exceptional customer experiences,
                        allowing you to focus on building lasting customer relationships.
                    </p>
